cloudmusic.help: The configuration file is in the game directory config/cloud_music_config
cloudmusic.help.playlist.add: add music to playlist /cloudmusic playlist add [id] [music id]
cloudmusic.help.playlist.del: Delete music from playlist /cloudmusic playlist del [id] [music id]
cloudmusic.help.artist.top: Play top 50 songs by artist /cloudmusic artist top [id]
cloudmusic.help.artist.album: See all albums by the artist /cloudmusic artist album [id]
cloudmusic.help.album.unsubscribe: Unsubscribe from the album /cloudmusic album unsubscribe [id]
cloudmusic.help.user.like: Get user's favorite music /cloudmusic user like [id]
cloudmusic.help.my.recommend.music: Recommended music of the day /cloudmusic my recommend music
cloudmusic.help.my.recommend.playlist: Daily recommended playlists /cloudmusic my recommend playlist
cloudmusic.help.my.sublist.album: My favorite albums /cloudmusic my sublist album
cloudmusic.help.my.sublist.artist: My favorite artists /cloudmusic my sublist artist
cloudmusic.help.login.country.code: Set cell phone number country code /cloudmusic login country [country code]
cloudmusic.help.login.captcha: Send mobile verification code /cloudmusic login captcha [mobile number]
cloudmusic.help.login.captcha.login: Cell phone verification code login /cloudmusic login captcha [cell phone number] [verification code]
cloudmusic.help.login.captcha.phone: Phone password login /cloudmusic login phone [phone number] [password]
cloudmusic.help.playing.all: View the list of playing music /cloudmusic playing all
